<br>
I can gain aggro, but it's completely unpredictable, and I can't intentionally hold it worth a damn.<br>
<br>
Mostly, I have just enough HP &amp; AC to avoid exploding instantly if something goes wrong and I come under fire <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
