<br>
BTW, at 60 bards can take a real beating, but they sing better when not being hit (less vibrato).  One of the most fun XP groups is to take a 60 bard and support group down to the disco area and do bard-AE.  You can clear all of D1, D2, and go out down the tunnel for more with a group like that.  Bards rock.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showMessageRange?topicID=52.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showMessageRange?topicID=52.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showMessageRange?topicID=52.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a> <b>4</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showPrevMessage?topicID=52.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showNextMessage?topicID=52.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=52.topic&index=62><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.threadControl?topicID=52.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=52.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard